# Trojan hub: 11 coders.
# Coder 1 is the hub with weight 1001 — rivals with everyone else.
# Coders 2..11 each have weight 1000 and have no rivalries among themselves.
#
# Greedy by-weight alone picks the hub  -> total 1001  (bad)
# Correct optimal: pick coders 2..11    -> total 10000 (good)
#
# This tests that the heuristic doesn't get fooled by a single heavy hub.
11 10
1001 1000 1000 1000 1000 1000 1000 1000 1000 1000 1000
